HND Records finest act O2 Father drops his highly anticipated EP titled “Mercy” and it’s the biggest project on the street right now. <img src="https://notjustok.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/O2_Father_Featured_Image.jpg" alt="HND Records Presents: O2 Father - Mercy EP"/> HND Records Presents: O2 Father – Mercy EP This is coming few weeks after he dropped the massive hit single titled “Since I Was Born” his debut single under Demmie’s Vee former label. Kick-starting his career with Mercy EP, O2 Father has proved on this project that he is the next big talent to watch out for in the Nigeria’s music industry. Housing 6 solid tracks, the beautifully crafted piece of work starts off a track titled “Street”. The production credits of the “Mercy EP” features the likes of Killertunez, DJ Coublon and Izzyblaq. The EP “Mercy” detailed the several experiences in his life as he delivers an astonishing performance mixed with artistic brilliance. Get you speakers plugged and enjoy good music. Listen below and share your thoughts. STREAM ON DIGITAL STORES Get More Updates via Twitter – @Notjustok The post HND Records Presents: O2 Father – Mercy EP appeared first on Most Trusted Voice in Music & Afrobeats from Nigeria & Africa | Notjustok. Original Article Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.